## Early game

Voidgel Orb is a **Zariman regional drop**, best farmed at **Tuvul Commons**
running **Void Cascade**. It's an in-mission pickup with a relatively low
individual chance (roughly 9.76% as a mission reward roll), so plan on
running several Cascade rotations rather than expecting one per mission.

Because it's a resource pickup, a **Resource Drop Booster boosts your Orb
drop rate** — worth popping one if you're stacking up Zariman crafting
requirements in the same session.

## Mid & late game

**Steel Path Tuvul Commons** is the sustained late-game farm: tougher enemies
and longer Cascade rotations mean more roll opportunities per hour, and the
Steel Path Resource Drop Chance Booster stacks with a regular Resource Drop
Booster on every roll. Running full Cascade rotations back-to-back on Steel
Path is the most efficient way to stockpile Voidgel Orbs for Zariman gear and
Deimos/Zariman crafting alike.

